    • Method Detail

      • getShcp

        public int getShcp()
        Calculates the "Spelhandicap" for the player based on exact handicap, slope rating, course rating and course pars. Formula: Spelhandicap = Exakthandicap * (Slopevärde / 113) + (Banvärde - Banans par)
        Returns:
        Returns "Spelhandicap" in integer.

      • getExtraShots

        public int[] getExtraShots()
